title: Amy Opens Up About Her Dad’s Health + Bobby’s New Book Hits #1 On New York Times Best Sellers List

description:
Amy opens up about her dad’s cancer diagnosis and recent surgery. Bobby hits the New York Times Best Seller list for the second time. Also, Lunchbox and his wife tour the hospital she’ll be delivering Baby Box at!
